C+
C     C O M B . I N C
C
C     Character common variables for the FIT_ routines
C
C     BUFF     Is used to build up the 'line' for a single
C              header keyword.
C     MTERR    Holds the error description for the last TIO_
C              error code.
C     DEVICE   Holds the actual name of the output device in use.
C 
C                                  KS / CIT 11th Oct 1983
C     Modified:
C
C     28th Oct 1987.  DEVICE added.  Comments for MTERR reflect
C                     change to TIO_ from MTPCKG.  KS/AAO.
C     26th Jul 1994.  Make common blocks SAVE. HME / UoE, Starlink.
C+
      CHARACTER BUFF*80,MTERR*64,DEVICE*128
      COMMON /FIG_COMB/ BUFF,MTERR,DEVICE
      SAVE /FIG_COMB/
C
